tionfor this year's Olympics.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998233307, \"rank\": 1.7670076841716815e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 958, \"end\": 963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999938609, \"rank\": 5.744922784074081e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"tap\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"the monsters\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"the safety\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"apoint\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"contentionfor\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Olympics\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The river has historically been so polluted that swimming has been banned in it for a century.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The river\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"a century\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, ahead of the Olympics, Paris launched massive infrastructure improvements intended to make the water safe for holding open water swimming events.\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1152, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998233307, \"rank\": 1.7670076841716815e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"htt